# IDEs Y EDITORES
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# VS Code (mantener .vscode/ raíz, ignorar configuraciones personales)
.vscode/launch.json
.vscode/*.log

# IntelliJ IDEA / Eclipse (para Java)
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
.classpath
.project
.settings/
*.factorypath

